<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Again, everyone here focuses on the stats and fails to see the truly important things...the wt. and the rareness of these items make them a valuable resell or trade bait item... monks drool over anything WW... this and the cloak are two admittedly overpriced items if stats are looked at alone. But take into the difficulty in getting these to drop, THEN the difficulty in getting Karg to spawn while you are close by, THEN the fact that ANYONE who sees him on track or in person is making a beeline for him to kill or complete their own quests... THAT is where the value of these lies...anyone who sells these for less than a 100x profit on their 75pp investment (provided they can get the gloves at all) is underselling. Sold my last pair for 700pp and Chrysoberyl Talisman... fair exchange, for me.</font></td></tr></table>
